Text:
Classification: Game Show
Genre: Celebrities | Comedy
Status: TBD/On The Bubble
Network: Channel 4 ( United Kingdom)
Airs: Saturdays at 08:20 pm
Runtime: 60 Minutes
Premiere: September 15, 2012
Episode Order: 7

Comedy World Cup is a panel show hosted by David Tennant. He asks the questions as two teams of comedians battle it out to showcase their knowledge of comedy. The winners of each show progress to the next round of the competition, before the last two teams compete in the grand final for the Comedy World Cup title.
